<p>Rebecca opted to slip into a glamorous emerald gown, as they led the pack in celebrity arrivals, which also included Jason Alexander. </p>

<p>The 60-year-old Seinfeld opted for a casual look, as he rocked a grey button-down, jeans and a pair of sneakers. </p>

<p>Not long after, Blanca Blanco and John Savage appeared at the screening. </p>

